Prepared: 02-04-2026 | Version: FINAL PARA-STYLE v2
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

                    IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE FOR RAJASTHAN
                              AT JODHPUR / JAIPUR BENCH

                    CRIMINAL MISCELLANEOUS PETITION NO. _______ / 2026
              (Under Section 482 Cr.P.C. / Article 226 & 227, Constitution of India)

IN THE MATTER OF:

Hemraj Vardar, S/o _____________________, Director, M/s Praman Construction
